com.interpss.core.aclf

Interface Aclf3WBranch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Branch, Branch3W, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclf3WXfrAdaptation, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Acsc3WBranch, DStab3WBranch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Aclf3WBranchImpl, Acsc3WBranchImpl, DStab3WBranchImpl

    public interface Aclf3WBranch
extends Branch3W, IAclf3WXfrAdaptation
    A representation of the model object 'Aclf3 WXformer'. A wrapper of three 2W branches. It is used to representing both 3W xfr and 3W psXfr. It does not contain any actual data. The data is contained in the three 2W xfr/psXfr.

    The following features are supported:

    • Branch Code
    • Voltage Star Bus
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getAclf3WBranch()
